{"tid":264934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日女記者開記招控訴 「安倍御用記者」涉強姦阻調查","createTime":"2017-05-31T08:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T11:08:38.000Z","uid":29627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"72f02db4b340230ded0bbbdb6ac67d698392fbd7","tid":264934,"uid":29627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T08:53:23.000Z","msg":"與日本首相安倍晉三相熟的著名記者山口敬之捲入強姦風波。28歲女記者詩織周一在律師陪同下召開記者會，挺身指證2年前遭山口強姦，又稱警方雖然證據確鑿，卻因來自上頭的壓力將他放生。<br />\n<br />\n記者會在東京司法記者俱樂部舉行，詩織用上真名及真面目示人，在日本社會極為罕見，至於姓氏則因家人意願而未有公開。詩織在2013年讀書時經熟人介紹認識被譽為「安倍御用記者」的山口。2015年3月，詩織向時任TBS電視台美國華盛頓支局長的山口發電郵求職，表明「想在支局工作」，山口隨即相約她4月3日在東京見面。<br />\n<br />\n二人到訪串燒店後轉到壽司店，強調自己酒量好的詩織說在壽司店用膳時失去記憶，之後在劇痛中醒來，發現山口正強姦她。詩織說：「恢復意識時已是翌晨5時許，在酒店床上。我被脫光衣物，山口騎我身上，我面部朝天。」詩織馬上到醫院，並在同月9日向警方求助。<br />\n<br />\n詩織指警方在調查中錄取了的士司機及酒店門僮等的供詞、收集了內衣上的DNA樣本，閉路電視亦拍攝到詩織被山口抱入酒店的畫面。當局同年6月向山口發拘捕令，多名探員持拘捕令在成田機場等候山口回國準備將他拘捕，詩織指探員在電話中交代：「雖然現在山口在我面前走過，但收到來自上頭的指示，不能將他拘捕。我也要結束調查。」<br />\n<br />\n當局在同年8月26日將山口送檢，去年7月22日，當局以證據不足為由將他放生。詩織不服，於是向檢察審査會提出不服申訴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170531/large/1496199817_28d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170531%2Flarge%2F1496199817_28d3.jpg&h=97ef83ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170531/56759613\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170531%2F56759613&d=jl7n1qwn2WWIzNfmHyC6m9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=85001bf9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170531%2F56759613&h=f5a43645\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170531/56759613</a>"},{"pid":"5074170a55a7bdb2a511d2b8e1ffbbbff0880204","tid":264934,"uid":92783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T08:57:05.000Z","msg":"神咲詩織？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df06a88801dd6342c704ff52b1ca2d689558e32f","tid":264934,"uid":498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T08:59:25.000Z","msg":"美女記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ce29d6c07c1c41397c771d1e4e87a04c87d1b7","tid":264934,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:03:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a661e93b61e58802d230e745d56b1d3961387b","tid":264934,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:34:39.000Z","msg":"鷲哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b23e63c294f4389666b5321617a91daad88f3a","tid":264934,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb2afbc5fa888c4654fd139e14377a341d289a4","tid":264934,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:53:24.000Z","msg":"連登仔:勞資糾紛"},{"pid":"79fd626cf394b5bfb1243f179a73d0f5312e71f2","tid":264934,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:56:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3bd3c2c4f22bb6814410ad7152da7756fa66deb8","tid":264934,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T09:58:30.000Z","msg":"真係Av劇情，<br />\n男人係咸濕中坑，<br />\n女係靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji